item.dc:creator: @SilentCJ SilentCJ
item.description:
@SilentCJ wrote:

Search 34000 in your main.java.
Change 34000 to about 10 past the id your rsmv is stuck on.
For example, if it gets stuck on 40000, change the 34000 to 40010, compile, and run it again.

If that doesn’t work, try changing it to 100 past the id it’s stuck on, and so on.
